#INTERNAL CSS STYLING

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="ISO-8859-1">
<title>CSS styling code</title>
<style>
body {
	background-color: blue;
	text-align: center;
	}
h1 {
	color: white;
	text-align: centre;
	}
h2 {
	color: pink;
	text-align: left;
	margin-left:40px;
	}
p {
	color: yellow;
	text-align: center;
	}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1> This is h1 tag!</h1>
<br>
<h2> This is h2 tag!</h2>
<br>
<p> This is paragraph!
Internal styles are defined within the 
style element, inside the head section of an HTML page.
</p>
</body>
</html>
